  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "binomial-theorem",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/binomial-theorem/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.56,
      "size": 40896,
      "text": "先看最熟悉的完全平方：(a+b)的平方，等于 a方加二ab加b方。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "binomial-theorem",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/binomial-theorem/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.99,
      "size": 31824,
      "text": "三项，系数分别是一、二、一，藏着漂亮的规律。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "binomial-theorem",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/binomial-theorem/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.9,
      "size": 30384,
      "text": "如果指数变成三、四、五，展开式又长什么样呢？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "binomial-theorem",
      "section_id": "coeff",
      "line_id": "coeff-1",
      "filename": "coeff-coeff-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/binomial-theorem/xiaoxiao/coeff-coeff-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.69,
      "size": 27072,
      "text": "展开 (a+b) 的 n 次方，会得到 n 加一项。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "binomial-theorem",
      "section_id": "coeff",
      "line_id": "coeff-2",
      "filename": "coeff-coeff-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/binomial-theorem/xiaoxiao/coeff-coeff-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.79,
      "size": 44640,
      "text": "每一项里，a 的指数从 n 递减，b 的指数从零递增，两者之和始终是 n。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "binomial-theorem",
      "section_id": "coeff",
      "line_id": "coeff-3",
      "filename": "coeff-coeff-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/binomial-theorem/xiaoxiao/coeff-coeff-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.76,
      "size": 28224,
      "text": "真正神奇的是前面的系数，它们排成了一个三角形。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "binomial-theorem",
      "section_id": "pascal",
      "line_id": "pascal-1",
      "filename": "pascal-pascal-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/binomial-theorem/xiaoxiao/pascal-pascal-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.56,
      "size": 24912,
      "text": "这就是帕斯卡三角，我们也叫它杨辉三角。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "binomial-theorem",
      "section_id": "pascal",
      "line_id": "pascal-2",
      "filename": "pascal-pascal-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/binomial-theorem/xiaoxiao/pascal-pascal-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32256,
      "text": "每个数，都等于它上方左右两个数之和，两端永远是一。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "binomial-theorem",
      "section_id": "pascal",
      "line_id": "pascal-3",
      "filename": "pascal-pascal-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/binomial-theorem/xiaoxiao/pascal-pascal-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.92,
      "size": 30672,
      "text": "第 n 行，正好就是 (a+b) 的 n 次方的全部系数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "binomial-theorem",
      "section_id": "combo",
      "line_id": "combo-1",
      "filename": "combo-combo-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/binomial-theorem/xiaoxiao/combo-combo-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.32,
      "size": 37152,
      "text": "为什么是这些数？因为系数其实是组合数 C(n,k)。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "binomial-theorem",
      "section_id": "combo",
      "line_id": "combo-2",
      "filename": "combo-combo-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/binomial-theorem/xiaoxiao/combo-combo-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.27,
      "size": 36288,
      "text": "把 n 个括号相乘，每一项就是从中选 k 个贡献 b、其余贡献 a。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "binomial-theorem",
      "section_id": "combo",
      "line_id": "combo-3",
      "filename": "combo-combo-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/binomial-theorem/xiaoxiao/combo-combo-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.6,
      "size": 41616,
      "text": "选法有 C(n,k) 种，于是这一项的系数就是 C(n,k)。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "binomial-theorem",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/binomial-theorem/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.89,
      "size": 30240,
      "text": "切换指数 n，看高亮行如何在三角中上下移动。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "binomial-theorem",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/binomial-theorem/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.89,
      "size": 30240,
      "text": "对照下方的展开式，感受系数与三角行的一一对应。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "binomial-theorem",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/binomial-theorem/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 30960,
      "text": "二项式定理把 (a+b) 的 n 次方展开成 n 加一项。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "binomial-theorem",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/binomial-theorem/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.72,
      "size": 27504,
      "text": "系数是组合数，恰好是帕斯卡三角的第 n 行。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "binomial-theorem",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/binomial-theorem/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.75,
      "size": 28080,
      "text": "一个三角形串起了代数与组合，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
